Package: QuickLahman
Type: Package
Title: Helper Functions for Easy Use of the Lahman Baseball Database
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Patrick", "Aabram",
      email = "patrick.w.aabram@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package contains various data manipulation functions to make the tables in
     the Sean 'Lahman' Baseball Database package more convenient to use, 
    specifically focused on the tables having to do with Major League player 
    statistics. Also adds some functions for stat calculation beyond the 
    battingStats() function in the original package.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), Lahman, dplyr
License: GPL (>= 3)
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Encoding: UTF-8
